      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a pinnacle of JZA80 engineering. This example features the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six, paired with the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain remains in factory-spec configuration, utilizing the original Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. Mechanically flawless, the engine bay shows no signs of heat-soak or fluid seepage, with all OEM vacuum lines and heat shielding intact. The chassis retains its high-rigidity integrity, supported by the stock double-wishbone suspension geometry. A rare, unmodified survivor in true concours-level condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
